import emoji1 from './images/angryface.png'
import emoji2 from './images/annoyedface.png'
import emoji3 from './images/laughingface.png'
import emoji4 from './images/lovelyface.png'
import emoji5 from './images/moneyface.png'
import emoji6 from './images/nerdface.png'
import emoji7 from './images/partyface.png'
import emoji8 from './images/sillyface.png'


const emojis = [
    { id: 0, src: emoji1 },
    { id: 1, src: emoji2 },
    { id: 2, src: emoji3 },
    { id: 3, src: emoji4 },
    { id: 4, src: emoji5 },
    { id: 5, src: emoji6 },
    { id: 6, src: emoji7 },
    { id: 7, src: emoji8 }
]

export default emojis;
